examples.en: Television is ruining the art of conversation.
He babbled on and on about how he was ruining me.
She wanted to get her own back on Liz for ruining her party.
He knocked over the red wine, thereby ruining the table cloth
'This government is ruining the country!' 'You're not wrong there!'
In her screed against the recording industry, she blamed her producer for ruining her career.
